FBIS4-36273 "drnes110_n_94009" FBIS-NES-94-110 Daily Report 8 Jun 1994 LEBANON Roundup of Military Activity in Southern Lebanon Roundup of Military Activity in Southern Lebanon `Resistance' Operation in Sujud NC0806082894 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0800 GMT 8 Jun 94 NC0806082894 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] The NATIONAL NEWS AGENCY office in al-Nabatiyah has reported that the Israeli occupation forces shelled al-Jabal al- Akhdar, al-Jabal al-Rafi', and al-Luwayzah in Iqlim al-Tuffah at 1030 today while Israeli warplanes flew over the al-Nabatiyah and Iqlim al-Tuffah areas. The resistance retaliated against the Israeli aggressions today by attacking the Sujud position with rockets and machine guns.
